snippet.title: TOKYO GHOUL: re CALL to EXIST - New York Comic Con Trailer | PS4, PC
snippet.description:
We heard you're hungry for more Tokyo Ghoul. Here are Kaneki, Touka, Amon, and more of your favorite characters as they fight in the war between Ghouls and Investigators.
